oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Johnny Morrison's Hay Barn Job No. 39763
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Carson, Martha;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 3229) for an order placed by Johnny Morrison's Hay Barn for 100 two color jumbos for a performance by Martha Carson at Johnny Morrison's Hay Barn in Shepherd, Texas on September 17. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
